snippet.title: Super Nova's Symphony Trailer
snippet.description:
Super Nova’s Symphony is a science fiction rhythm game with RPG elements where you play as Nova, a violinist onboard a space train on her way to a music tournament at the core of the universe. Explore cosy train cars as you challenge the travellers to music duels where you pull off button combinations in exciting rhythm sequences. Over the course of the journey, you will discover Nova’s past... and perhaps her true self.

Download for FREE: https://wavelengthstudios.itch.io/sns
Twitter: https://twitter.com/WavelengthStud1
